        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\nI see the following issues when testing:\n1. Change \"TOSCA_Type\" to \"TOSCA Type\" in the filters on left hand side\n2. There are only 35 elements shown in the catalog even when there are more elements than this\n3. Search button in top right does not seem to work on the data types\n4. Ordering does not seem to work - i.e. if I checkout a VFC I would expect to see it top of the list when ordered by last updated, but it is not\n5. Only data types from SDC model shown (i.e. none shown when ETSI model selected)\n6. Model name not shown on tile",
